resources.string: Igama lakho lisetshenziselwa ukwenza ithebhulethi yakho nezinsizakalo ze-Google zibe ezakho siqu.
Lethebhulethi isebenzisa igama lakho ukwenza ezinye izinsiza ieyakho siqu.
Ithebulethi yakho ixhumana no-Google ukuze ungene kwi-akhawunti yakho. Lokhu kungathatha amaminithi ayisi-5.

"Ithebhulethi yakho ixhumana no-Google ukubona ukuthi igama lomsebenzisi olifisayo liyatholakala yini.
Lokhu kungathatha imizuzu embalwa.."
"Iqoqa ulwazi mayelana nethebhulethi yakho. Lokhu kungathatha amasekhondi angama-30."

"Sebenzisa i-akhawunti yakho yakwa-Google ukulondoloza izinsiza zakho, izilungiselelo (ezifana namabhukumaka kanye namaphasiwedi e-Wi-Fi), kanye nenye idatha. Uma uke walondoloza i-akhawunti yakho phambilini, ungayibuyisela kulekhompyutha yepeni njengamanje.
Ungazishintsha izilungiselelo zakho zokulondoloza noma nini Ezilungiselelweni."

"Sebenzisa i-akhawunti yakho yakwa-Google ukulondoloza izinsiza zakho, kanye nezilungiselelo ezifana namabhukumaka kanye namaphasiwedi e-Wi-Fi), kanye neminye imininingwane.
Ungazishintsha izisetho zakho zokulondoloza noma inini Ezilungiselelweni."
Gcina lethebhulethi ilondoloziwe nge-akhawuntini yami ye-Google
Buyisela kusuka e-akhawuntini yami yakwa-Google kuye kulethebhulethi
Ithebulethi yakho ixhumana no-Google ukuze ubuyise i-akhawunti yakho. Lokhu kungathatha imizuzu emi-5.
